{"tid":2258263,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潘媽媽餘生只剩討回公道 憶曉穎夢中呐喊：救命有冇人幫我！","createTime":"2020-10-26T01:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T07:19:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d18da3edc0d787c167b519957d15d85400dc08d8","tid":2258263,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"「媽咪真係好唔捨得你，我同你只係相處20年你就走咗，你知唔知我成日都掛住你？我寧願用我條命交換。」台灣殺人案死者潘曉穎的母親，在重陽節帶來鮮花拜祭女兒，告訴她疑兇陳同佳仍未履行赴台投案自首的壞消息。愛女兩年多前遭殘殺棄屍，，自此潘媽媽的生活出現翻天巨變。近日她四出奔波無果，面對冷漠政權令她十分氣餒，但每當想起夢中無助及虛弱的女兒，她便打起精神，許諾下半生唯一目標就是要為愛女討回公道。她看着手機內女兒的相片，幽幽的說「我哋行緊條路係好崎嶇，好難行，無論點樣我都要幫你沉冤得雪，你知唔知道你條命係我好辛苦先至生到你出嚟，我係唔會就咁放棄，你聽到嘛？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/NRLU2KHLFRH7VFOVGYMBLWFJBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FNRLU2KHLFRH7VFOVGYMBLWFJBQ%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=10c48d81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FNRLU2KHLFRH7VFOVGYMBLWFJBQ%2F&h=7dd31656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/NRLU2KHLFRH7VFOVGYMBLWFJBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"68a30c0df216f62756f7619354d079d44c7cb644","tid":2258263,"uid":201414,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"阿佳：吹呀 我唔去台灣你吹得我脹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e994e9e70b3b1e4ff1a3da3fafe5fdb4e4410bd7","tid":2258263,"uid":11809,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:55:21.000Z","msg":"林奠：唔好提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51604550c05eeb0d8afde9acdafaff58867a2217","tid":2258263,"uid":198841,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"希望你餘生搵到個話得事既人同你傾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b52a80b0ecd18cc1d2446fef2c5f5446aa59c5","tid":2258263,